{"tid":2370612,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"3人擲竹枝到東鐵線路軌　危及他人安全罪成 分被判入更生及監禁10個月","createTime":"2021-01-18T07:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T09:26:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a0952e444f1e52b4f085b6e89d33494d205b3adf","tid":2370612,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:13:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13002&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=c8d2c465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13002</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#黃國輝裁判官<br />\n#1111大埔 #鐵路罪行 #判刑 <br />\n<br />\nD1王(18)<br />\nD5何(22)<br />\nD6郭(28)<br />\n<br />\n【控罪】<br />\n(7)危害他人安全（控罪(1)的交替控罪）<br />\n（第556章《香港鐵路條例》第30條；最高刑罰罰款$100,000及監禁3年）<br />\n<br />\n❌被告全不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n早前另外3名被告已認罪（D2D4 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8591&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=c50f6c18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8591</a>)，D3 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8580&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=ce665afa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8580</a>) ），D7罪名不成立；<br />\n審訊內容（1 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12784&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=d5a9dcb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12784</a>)、2 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12787&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=9f30abc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12787</a>)、3 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12789&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=abe52836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12789</a>)、4 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12792&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=c4aa2bad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12792</a>)、5 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12794&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=5198c545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12794</a>)）；<br />\n裁決 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12893&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=b79b5759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12893</a>)。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n辯方律師求情<br />\n<br />\n🔸d1辯方🔸<br />\n更生中心報告顯示，被告適合去更生中心，認為能夠幫助被告守法，加強其概念，被告同意內容。<br />\n<br />\n🔸d5辯方🔸<br />\n背景報告顯示正面，講述被告自小成績良好，操行優質，家人也會一直支持被告。<br />\n<br />\n🔸d6辯方🔸<br />\n背景報告顯示極度正面，家庭各人關係融洽，被告會支付自己額外進修讀書的費用，也有給予家用父母，希望法庭能給予機會被告重投社會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n判刑<br />\n法庭表示判刑時考慮以下各點：<br />\n本案案情、辯方求情內容、上一次求情內容、更生、背景報告及各人沒有任何刑事紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n法庭認為一群人將4，50枝竹枝拋擲在鐵路路軌，非常嚴重，竹枝的高度厚度及其堅硬程度，從高處掉下一定會影響鐵路及他人的安全。東鐵綫日常運作相當大，任何人將這些竹枝拋擲在路軌上必然嚴重影響了鐵路運輸系統。因此，法庭必須判處阻嚇性懲罰。<br />\n<br />\nd5d6乃成年人，本席採納11個月監禁作量刑起點，本案經審訊後定罪故沒有減刑因素，基於2被告紀錄良好，扣減1個月，最後判處即時監禁10個月‼️<br />\n<br />\nd1年輕，且紀錄良好，本席採納更生中心‼️讓被告接受有紀錄性的訓練。"},{"pid":"9de991f2bc46e60c14157d7fc4d566a7178c0cbc","tid":2370612,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b89758fd76726a8b2bfb0026c6c0d0cbdcaec6","tid":2370612,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:17:08.000Z","msg":"跳軌果班又唔見你告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca692dc21d89b4d00234dd0f864f2f9863c4eb5","tid":2370612,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0cf401ba48517a044ad0f8432d28ce51180e5e","tid":2370612,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d599263453d8b3434ae214d59d0e563a351487","tid":2370612,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ec38cd7f3cbb2c37c024ee1fcf7adc3088920d","tid":2370612,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"十個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aa3456e0ea781ec1ae5fb7975a67349b798b2d","tid":2370612,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42e67e873da71f24477f86c44a627644abcac14","tid":2370612,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"義務急救員無做過野就坐4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb57f05ee21e2612589563f62fea34e9b0770f3","tid":2370612,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0144e6672ab91a717602eee057db9d6a1c4dac0e","tid":2370612,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef559269468f5a534d1c243b8da8e66e6b02dbf","tid":2370612,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"兩男一女於前年11 月11日向東鐵綫大埔段路軌投擲竹枝，被裁定危及他人安全罪名成立。裁判官黃國輝今日判刑指，三人觸犯的控罪情節嚴重，由高處將既大且重又硬的竹枝抛落路軌，嚴重影響鐵路系統，必須判以阻嚇性刑罰。案中兩男犯案時已成年，法庭以11個月監禁為量刑起點，基於過往紀錄良好，酌情扣減一個月，判囚10個月。而女被告犯案時只有16歲，因此接納報告建議，判入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n首被告的報告認為更生中心是適合刑罰，能夠幫助加強她的守法意識。而次被告的大律師則指，背景報告內容正面，被告過往讀書成績好、操行佳，在數學方面有天份，因此才可升讀科大，希望法庭考慮到他的優良品格，予以輕判。第三被告的大律師則指其背景報告內容正面，與家人關係和睦，希望法庭給予他重投社會的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/XOQT6222YJEPVPFGVUYLJJTAFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FXOQT6222YJEPVPFGVUYLJJTAFM%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=5caf004f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FXOQT6222YJEPVPFGVUYLJJTAFM%2F&h=a12777e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/XOQT6222YJEPVPFGVUYLJJTAFM/</a>"},{"pid":"61dd84660f42ecc5147e96e9e0b9578e54be9078","tid":2370612,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90110833eda879bdbe3d6c826596d638a63348b5","tid":2370612,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"eef559269468f5a534d1c243b8da8e66e6b02dbf","tid":2370612,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"兩男一女於前年11 月11日向東鐵綫大埔段路軌投擲竹枝，被裁定危及他人安全罪名成立。裁判官黃國輝今日判刑指，三人觸犯的控罪情節嚴重，由高處將既大且重又硬的竹枝抛落路軌，嚴重影響鐵路系統，必須判以阻嚇性刑罰。案中兩男犯案時已成年，法庭以11個月監禁為量刑起點，基於過往紀錄良好，酌情扣減一個月，判囚10個月。而女被告犯案時只有16歲，因此接納報告建議，判入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n首被告的報告認為更生中心是適合刑罰，能夠幫助加強她的守法意識。而次被告的大律師則指，背景報告內容正面，被告過往讀書成績好、操行佳，在數學方面有天份，因此才可升讀科大，希望法庭考慮到他的優良品格，予以輕判。第三被告的大律師則指其背景報告內容正面，與家人關係和睦，希望法庭給予他重投社會的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/XOQT6222YJEPVPFGVUYLJJTAFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FXOQT6222YJEPVPFGVUYLJJTAFM%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=5caf004f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210118%2FXOQT6222YJEPVPFGVUYLJJTAFM%2F&h=a12777e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210118/XOQT6222YJEPVPFGVUYLJJTAFM/</a>"}}